#, fuzzy
msgid "This description in the change note should be a high level \"marketing\" summary of the change from the perspective of the user, not a deep technical description or implementation detail. It is distinct from a commit message - a commit message describes what has been done so that future developers can follow the reasoning for a change; the change note is a description for the benefit of users, who may not have knowledge of internals."
