msgid "You can highlight multiple different lines. For example, `python {hl_lines=\"3 5 9\"}` would highlight lines 3, 5 and 9. You can also highlight a range of lines. For example, `python {hl_lines=\"3-8\"}` highlights lines 3 through 8. You can highlight multiple ranges with, for example, `python {hl_lines=\"9-18 23-44\"}`."
